{"id": 2220, "genre": 1001, "title": "你心目中富有魅力的成熟女性应该是啥样的？", "description": "国人眼里的女性形象，除了 young girl 就是 old woman，从青春可爱到聒噪讨嫌无缝切换，mature 这一档，不存在的。（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 2672, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201803121315262fEiPqF8VGxCdw0U.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-13T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 270592, "content": "刚", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285585}, {"id": 271104, "content": "自信优雅，推荐一个我女神，艾玛.沃森，超喜欢她的(虽然我也是女的)哈利波特里演赫敏\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272761}, {"id": 270337, "content": "就像“萧剑”这个名字的含义那样，诗意却锋利。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011810}, {"id": 270338, "content": "美而不自知", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686468}, {"id": 270339, "content": "自信 睿智 独立思想 不盲从 能完整感受和理解人或事物的多面性", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263864}, {"id": 270595, "content": "独立，气质，自信 不矫情", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 884017}, {"id": 273667, "content": "内外兼修", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1300592}, {"id": 270340, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241445}, {"id": 270341, "content": "勇敢、好奇。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254180}, {"id": 270342, "content": "让人想靠近", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241445}, {"id": 270343, "content": "挪威的森林里的初美   娴静优雅，善解人意", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831413}, {"id": 270344, "content": "优雅", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266505}, {"id": 270345, "content": "俞飞鸿", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527822}, {"id": 270601, "content": "去看看我老婆的恋爱回旋你就知道了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1263459}, {"id": 270858, "content": "善良温厚大度从容", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284639}, {"id": 270347, "content": "时尚却不物质，个性却不任性！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284644}, {"id": 270348, "content": "自信", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281000}, {"id": 270349, "content": "天使与圣母之间有平衡。哈哈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1257000}, {"id": 270350, "content": "包容，衣着与妆容得体", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812813}, {"id": 270351, "content": "伊莎贝尔·于佩尔", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1271700}, {"id": 270607, "content": "对生活不失望，优雅气质，观念端正", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285216}, {"id": 270096, "content": "博学多才，睿智聪颖，温婉如玉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284114}, {"id": 270352, "content": "美得自成一派，隐藏很深的实力，真实且自尊自爱，生来就是风景。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284667}, {"id": 270097, "content": "自立自强，工作专业，非绿茶非心机婊，不当小三", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1207675}, {"id": 270353, "content": "独立思考，这一点就已足够", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 271121, "content": "独立有主见 洒脱懂自律 善良有头脑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289495}, {"id": 270098, "content": "知道自己想要什么并为之努力", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038451}, {"id": 270099, "content": "靠自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156224}, {"id": 270355, "content": "脑子里蹦出来几个名字：周轶君，崔卫平，梁晓燕，查建英，王安忆", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281562}, {"id": 270100, "content": "能力过硬而温和礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 375, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913212}, {"id": 270356, "content": "童颜巨乳", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956627}, {"id": 271124, "content": "刘涛！头脑第一名为就是她，知性优雅又有气质，（银幕形象）贤妻良母的形象，满足了我对另一半的所有需求。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289534}, {"id": 270101, "content": "像女王天海佑希在around 40里的那样，有自己的心爱的事业，保有独立人格，不以他人的价值观来判断自己的生活，有生活追求，既可以享受孤独，也可以和三五好友交心，对未来抱有希望。", "image": null, "praise_count": 235, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113539}, {"id": 271125, "content": "有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 714940}, {"id": 271637, "content": "对自己的爱恨很满\n接受自己并遵从内心\n任何时候都有改变自我的本事和魄力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291120}, {"id": 270102, "content": "周韵，又少女又成熟。", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284130}, {"id": 270358, "content": "傲骨贤妻里的Diane", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284685}, {"id": 270359, "content": "赵敏", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668175}, {"id": 270615, "content": "第一反应就是西西里的美丽传说里的女主角～太有魅力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285429}, {"id": 270104, "content": "在社会上不依赖任何人可以自在生活，无论是物质还是精神上。在生活里与人相伴的时候也可以小鸟依人，享受生活，跟自己志同道合的朋友一起享受旅行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284127}, {"id": 270360, "content": "不用刻意强调女性气质，成熟的有魅力的人无论男女或其他都有相同的特质。理性，独立，尊重别人，open-minded等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154367}, {"id": 270616, "content": "萧红", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285658}, {"id": 277272, "content": "同意我右边的同志\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275677}, {"id": 270105, "content": "不盲从  有自己的主见 能平衡好生活和事业", "image": null, "praise_count": 477, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966594}, {"id": 270361, "content": "做自己想做的事情，爱自己喜欢的人，不被世俗的婚姻观束缚，想要嫁就什么时候嫁什么时候。\n独立，自信，自强，上进，用行动诠释女权。\n不需要有多好看。我认为一个人的外表是会被ta的内在气质影响的。不会因为自己的外表而自卑或是自满，活出自信美就好。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145482}, {"id": 270617, "content": "美丽 坚强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702963}, {"id": 270106, "content": "Sex and the city的Samantha ", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698040}, {"id": 270618, "content": "现实中的江一燕，电视剧里的罗玥吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285660}, {"id": 270107, "content": "纸牌屋里的Claire", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304619}, {"id": 270363, "content": "反而有颗少女心", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085968}]}